### API Examples for Globe Wanderer Backend
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ========================================
### Authentication
### ========================================

### Login Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@globewanderer.com",
  "password": "Admin@123456"
}

### Get Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Change Password
PUT {{baseUrl}}/auth/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "Admin@123456",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword@123"
}

### ========================================
### Locations
### ========================================

### Get All Locations (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/locations

### Get Active Locations Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/locations?isActive=true

### Get Location by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/locations/location-id-here

### Get Location by Slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/locations/slug/ha-noi

### Create Location (Auth Required)
POST {{baseUrl}}/locations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Đà Nẵng",
  "slug": "da-nang",
  "description": "Thành phố đáng sống với biển đẹp và ẩm thực phong phú",
  "seoTitle": "Du lịch Đà Nẵng - Thành phố biển đẹp nhất Việt Nam",
  "seoDescription": "Khám phá Đà Nẵng với tour du lịch, khách sạn resort giá tốt",
  "isActive": true
}

### Update Location (Auth Required)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/locations/location-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated description",
  "isActive": true
}

### Delete Location (Auth Required)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/locations/location-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========================================
### Properties
### ========================================

### Get All Properties
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties

### Filter Properties by Location
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties?locationId=location-id-here

### Filter Properties by Type
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties?type=hotel

### Filter Active Properties
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties?isActive=true

### Get Property by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties/property-id-here

### Create Property (Auth Required)
POST {{baseUrl}}/properties
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "InterContinental Danang Sun Peninsula Resort",
  "locationId": "location-id-here",
  "type": "hotel",
  "description": "Resort 5 sao sang trọng tại Đà Nẵng",
  "basePrice": 4500000,
  "maxGuests": 2,
  "images": [
    "https://example.com/image1.jpg",
    "https://example.com/image2.jpg"
  ],
  "amenities": [
    "WiFi miễn phí",
    "Bể bơi vô cực",
    "Spa & Wellness",
    "Nhà hàng cao cấp",
    "Beach club"
  ],
  "isActive": true
}

### Update Property (Auth Required)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/properties/property-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "basePrice": 5000000,
  "isActive": true
}

### Delete Property (Auth Required)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/properties/property-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========================================
### Bookings
### ========================================

### Create Booking (Public - Customer Endpoint)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Trần Thị B",
  "phone": "0987654321",
  "email": "customer@example.com",
  "locationId": "location-id-here",
  "propertyId": "property-id-here",
  "checkIn": "2025-03-01",
  "checkOut": "2025-03-03",
  "guests": 2,
  "totalPrice": 9000000,
  "note": "Yêu cầu phòng view biển"
}

### Get All Bookings (Auth Required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filter Bookings by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings?status=pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filter Bookings by Location
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings?locationId=location-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filter Bookings by Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings?startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Booking Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Booking by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/booking-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Booking Details (Auth Required)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/bookings/booking-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "guests": 3,
  "totalPrice": 10500000,
  "note": "Khách yêu cầu thêm giường phụ"
}

### Update Booking Status (Auth Required)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/bookings/booking-id-here/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "confirmed",
  "adminNote": "Đã xác nhận với khách hàng qua điện thoại",
  "paidAmount": 3000000
}

### Update Payment (Auth Required)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/bookings/booking-id-here/payment
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paidAmount": 9000000
}

### Delete Booking (Auth Required)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/bookings/booking-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========================================
### Dashboard
### ========================================

### Get Dashboard Overview
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Overview with Date Filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/overview?startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Revenue by Location
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/revenue/by-location
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Revenue by Property
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/revenue/by-property
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Revenue by Property for Specific Location
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/revenue/by-property?locationId=location-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Monthly Revenue for 2025
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/revenue/by-month?year=2025
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Top 10 Properties
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/top-properties?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Recent Bookings
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/recent-bookings?limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========================================
### Booking Status Values
### ========================================

# - pending: Chờ xử lý
# - contacted: Đã liên hệ
# - confirmed: Đã xác nhận
# - paid: Đã thanh toán
# - completed: Hoàn thành (tính revenue)
# - cancelled: Đã hủy

### ========================================
### Property Types
### ========================================

# - hotel: Khách sạn
# - homestay: Homestay
# - tour: Tour du lịch
# - cruise: Du thuyền
